Parameters:
categoryLearningId - Id of the music category which is used for training
categoryOptimizationId - Id of the music category which is used for independent optimization
categoryTestId - Id of the music category which is used for independent evaluation
algorithmDescription - Id of optimization algorithm from optimizerAlgorithmTable.arff
continueOldExperimentFrom - Path to file with previous unfinished experiment to continue from (otherwise "-1", which is default value)
destinationFolder - Folder for optimization results
